rComments: Great professor! Don't take this class if you wanna fail!

Pay attention in lectures, and you barely have to do any of the reading. Class is 4 3 page papers, 2 6 page papers, an open-book midterm exam, and an 11ish page easy final project. When you talk to her at office hours she can be long-winded but what she tells you is very helpful. Good grades if you spit back out what she said earlier. Not hard.
